    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr><td colspan="3">&nbsp;</td></tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="3" align="left">
		
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			
				
					Damage:&nbsp; </font><font face="verdana" size="2" color="white">8&nbsp;&nbsp;</font>
					<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">Delay:&nbsp;</font> <font face="verdana" size="2" color="white">35&nbsp;&nbsp;</font>
					<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">Range:&nbsp; <font face="verdana" size="2" color="white">-&nbsp;&nbsp;</font>
					
					
		
		<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">Weight:&nbsp; </font><font face="verdana" size="2" color="white">8.0&nbsp;&nbsp;</font>
	
		
		 
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr><td colspan="3">&nbsp;</td></tr>
  <tr>
    <td width colspan="3" align="left" rowspan="7" valign="top"><font face="Verdana">
    The Screaming Mace is the result of a very long and difficult quest. The weapon randomly casts a spell that is similar to Yaulp II.
		
		
		
		</font></td>
    
  
	 	
