	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			The screaming mace quest have a few parts to complete this quest. It all takes place in Crush Bone. <BR>
<BR>
#1) Kill Emporer Crush Get his Dwarven Tunic (Magic Item)<BR>
#2) Find the Rare Spawning Warlord Kill him and hope He has the very rare Bracer of Battle.<BR>
#3) Give the tunic to the middle Dwarven Smith in the house by the Lego Camp. In return he gives you a Dwarven Mace (Non -Magical)<BR>
#4) Give the Bracer of Battle to the Elven Priest on the end. He will inturn give you a Prayr Cloth (Magic Sholders)<BR>
#5) Give just the Dwarven Mace to the Elven Priest. He will then Ask for something else. Only then do you give him the Prayer Cloth Sholders. He then gives you a screaming mace.<BR>
<BR>
Emporer Crush is about 18th Level<BR>
Orc Warlord is about 14-15th Level<BR>
<BR>
The items you get during this quest are all nice items and you may want to do this quest a few times to try and get them all.<BR>
<BR>

			</font>
	
		</td>
