			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Believe it or not, the room where D'vinn and Emperor Crush spawn is a reasonably safe place, at least on my server (Karana) -- the Throne Room and Table Room are so heavily camped that you're lucky to get the kill at all.  The only hard part about this quest is killing the Warlord for his Bracer.  A note to all you druids, the Prayer Cloth of Tunare is *very* worth keeping, as it is a +3 WIS shoulders.  Do the quest twice, even if you have to buy the Bracers..
			</font>
	
