			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Be careful with this quest.  I collected the tunic from Crush and the Bracers from the Warlord.  But when doing the swaps with the smithy and priest, I fell prey to a bug.  With Dwarven mace in hand, I gave the bracers to the priest.  He gave me a pat on the back, the experience, and told me the cloth as well.  However, he did not in fact give me the cloth.  The result is that I end up having to camp for the bracers again as without the cloth from the priest, no screaming mace.<BR>
<BR>
I've submitted this issue to Verant and have yet to hear back.  Here is hoping that they take care of the bug and provide me with my mace.<BR>
<BR>
In case it is a server thing, I'm on Quellious.  Be advised.<BR>
<BR>
Gavilion 20th Paladin
